Generic single-database configuration for PagePay backend.

## Create a new migration

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"
```

## Apply migrations

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

## Rollback migrations

```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

## Show current revision

```bash
alembic current
```

## Show migration history

```bash
alembic history
```
